      <title>英美资源集团收到必和必拓收购提议，可能重塑铜市场</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-considering-potential-buyout-offer-anglo-american-bloomberg-reports-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦上市矿业公司英美资源集团周四表示，已收到必和必拓集团的全股收购提议，该交易将使这家全球最大的上市矿业公司同时成为全球最大的铜生产商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bhp-considering-potential-buyout-offer-anglo-american-bloomberg-reports-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 21:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
